1
00:01:17,210 --> 00:01:19,212
Day 34 of observing Eun-seo

2
00:01:19,279 --> 00:01:21,014
via the smart home system,

3
00:01:21,715 --> 00:01:24,451
and behavior observation cams.

4
00:01:25,218 --> 00:01:27,287
The cause of her symptoms

5
00:01:27,354 --> 00:01:28,388
may have stemmed

6
00:01:29,957 --> 00:01:34,628
from the panic
disorder five years ago,

7
00:01:35,295 --> 00:01:36,697
after our mother's passing,

8
00:01:37,831 --> 00:01:40,734
and the stress of moving

9
00:01:41,468 --> 00:01:45,906
along with the stress
of practicing all day

10
00:01:45,973 --> 00:01:47,741
for her audition by herself.

11
00:02:37,057 --> 00:02:39,793
(Lucifer: A fallen
angel who rules Hell)

12
00:02:41,261 --> 00:02:44,131
(Moloch: A demon that
devours child sacrifices)

13
00:02:45,332 --> 00:02:48,101
(Beelzebul: Chief
lieutenant of Lucifer)

14
00:02:49,536 --> 00:02:52,305
(Valac: A fallen angel who
became Hell's guardian)

15
00:02:53,573 --> 00:02:55,308
(Archbishop: Leader
of the worshipers)

16
00:02:55,375 --> 00:02:56,910
(overseeing the entire ritual)

17
00:02:58,245 --> 00:03:01,715
(Worshippers:
Followers of the Devil)

18
00:03:04,918 --> 00:03:06,853
(Exorcism: The act
of freeing someone)

19
00:03:06,920 --> 00:03:08,955
(from possession
by an evil spirit)

20
00:03:24,504 --> 00:03:28,108
(Holy Night: Demon Hunters)

21
00:03:31,945 --> 00:03:33,447
All done!

22
00:03:34,681 --> 00:03:35,615
Evening, Kim.

23
00:03:35,682 --> 00:03:36,993
- Det. Choi, welcome.
- Good evening.

24
00:03:37,017 --> 00:03:37,951
Hey, Sharon.

25
00:03:38,018 --> 00:03:39,720
- Is Bow in?
- Yes, he is.

26
00:03:40,220 --> 00:03:41,421
He's a client.

27
00:03:42,155 --> 00:03:43,590
- Good evening.
- Hello.

28
00:03:43,657 --> 00:03:45,726
You may go inside.

29
00:03:47,461 --> 00:03:49,362
Boss, Det. Choi is here.

30
00:03:55,669 --> 00:03:59,239
A month ago, my daughter
became unreachable,

31
00:03:59,306 --> 00:04:00,907
I think she went missing.

32
00:04:01,408 --> 00:04:03,343
She'd never just disappear.

33
00:04:03,410 --> 00:04:05,112
Something is
definitely wrong here.

34
00:04:05,746 --> 00:04:07,480
Three of my men were assaulted

35
00:04:07,547 --> 00:04:09,182
while searching for her.

36
00:04:09,783 --> 00:04:12,052
Two are dead, and one's in ICU.

37
00:04:12,953 --> 00:04:15,622
As usual, I need
your help on this.

38
00:04:15,689 --> 00:04:18,258
If the detectives were harmed,

39
00:04:18,325 --> 00:04:20,560
I realized it was more serious.

40
00:04:20,627 --> 00:04:21,961
So I asked him for a favor

41
00:04:22,028 --> 00:04:23,530
and came to you for help.

42
00:04:23,597 --> 00:04:25,298
Don't worry too much,

43
00:04:25,365 --> 00:04:27,801
we'll look into this case closely.

44
00:04:27,868 --> 00:04:29,769
Kim, get something to drink.

45
00:04:29,836 --> 00:04:31,271
Sure, one moment.

46
00:04:31,805 --> 00:04:32,805
I'm okay...

47
00:04:34,674 --> 00:04:35,709
Pardon me...

48
00:04:37,077 --> 00:04:38,344
Sorry about that.

49
00:04:38,411 --> 00:04:40,313
Do you have any leads?

50
00:04:40,881 --> 00:04:43,616
We secured a location
from a photo we obtained,

51
00:04:43,683 --> 00:04:45,051
but my team got attacked

52
00:04:45,118 --> 00:04:47,120
and we couldn't rescue her.

53
00:04:47,187 --> 00:04:48,388
Here, Sharon.

54
00:04:48,455 --> 00:04:50,156
- Here you go.
- Thank you.

55
00:04:50,223 --> 00:04:51,258
Thanks.

56
00:04:56,663 --> 00:04:58,131
- Go inside.
- Okay.

57
00:04:59,766 --> 00:05:01,334
Would you like some water?

58
00:05:05,405 --> 00:05:08,875
Don't worry, we'll do our best.

59
00:05:11,344 --> 00:05:12,679
Detective...

60
00:05:13,513 --> 00:05:16,282
Can I trust them...

61
00:05:16,349 --> 00:05:18,318
You can absolutely trust us.

62
00:05:19,019 --> 00:05:24,524
We may look shady,
but we're professionals.

63
00:05:25,725 --> 00:05:27,894
Please find her for me.

64
00:05:27,961 --> 00:05:29,729
- We'll do our best.
- Yes, sir.

65
00:05:29,796 --> 00:05:31,131
Thank you.

66
00:05:35,902 --> 00:05:37,637
Here's the payment,
in cash as usual.

67
00:05:38,572 --> 00:05:40,807
You didn't skimp some
like last time, right?

68
00:05:41,341 --> 00:05:43,076
What do you take me for?
I'm a cop.

69
00:05:43,910 --> 00:05:46,446
How many clients have
I brought you so far?

70
00:05:48,548 --> 00:05:49,783
For your kids.

71
00:05:50,917 --> 00:05:52,252
What do you take me for?

72
00:05:53,253 --> 00:05:54,087
Don't want it?

73
00:05:54,154 --> 00:05:55,689
This is serious.

74
00:05:56,456 --> 00:05:58,091
A lot of people have been killed.

75
00:05:58,158 --> 00:05:58,992
I hear you.

76
00:05:59,059 --> 00:06:00,994
All right, guys.

77
00:06:02,696 --> 00:06:03,964
Let's go to work.

78
00:06:30,423 --> 00:06:33,159
Murders and assaults
are taking place

79
00:06:33,226 --> 00:06:38,398
by unknown assailants
across the country,

80
00:06:38,465 --> 00:06:40,500
leaving the public in fear.

81
00:06:41,101 --> 00:06:44,704
The police believe
that a mysterious group,

82
00:06:44,771 --> 00:06:46,639
along with organized
criminals, are involved.

83
00:06:46,706 --> 00:06:49,642
A special task force
has been formed,

84
00:06:49,709 --> 00:06:51,144
but the criminals have

85
00:06:51,211 --> 00:06:54,147
brutally murdered
officers at the scene...

86
00:06:56,783 --> 00:06:59,986
In my 30 years as an officer,

87
00:07:00,487 --> 00:07:03,156
I've never seen such
vicious incidents, Father.

88
00:07:03,823 --> 00:07:07,560
They talk about demons and devils,

89
00:07:07,627 --> 00:07:10,096
and as we witness
unbelievable events,

90
00:07:10,163 --> 00:07:12,031
we can't handle this

91
00:07:12,098 --> 00:07:15,001
with the police
force alone, Father.

92
00:07:15,502 --> 00:07:17,503
They blindly devote themselves

93
00:07:17,570 --> 00:07:18,570
to a devil worship per,

94
00:07:19,072 --> 00:07:20,907
and obtained superhuman strength

95
00:07:20,974 --> 00:07:22,876
by drawing on the Devil's power.

96
00:07:24,044 --> 00:07:26,446
Ordinary people
can't stand up to them.

97
00:07:29,349 --> 00:07:32,185
That's why we need him.

98
00:09:39,712 --> 00:09:40,713
Kill them!

99
00:10:46,479 --> 00:10:48,781
You vile demon.

100
00:10:49,883 --> 00:10:52,185
I command you.

101
00:10:52,886 --> 00:10:54,754
Return to hell!

102
00:10:55,488 --> 00:10:57,990
You are Bael,
the Commander of Hell's Army.

103
00:10:58,057 --> 00:11:00,059
Return to hell at once!

104
00:11:00,126 --> 00:11:01,794
Return!

105
00:11:04,264 --> 00:11:08,201
I command you!

106
00:11:09,035 --> 00:11:11,737
Return to hell!

107
00:11:11,804 --> 00:11:13,640
Return to hell immediately!

108
00:11:15,208 --> 00:11:16,208
I command you.

109
00:11:29,556 --> 00:11:31,724
Return to hell.

110
00:11:32,926 --> 00:11:34,761
Return to hell immediately!

111
00:11:56,349 --> 00:11:57,584
Let's see.

112
00:12:00,119 --> 00:12:01,154
Okay.

113
00:12:03,456 --> 00:12:05,258
Everything all right?

114
00:12:05,325 --> 00:12:06,392
I'm fine.

115
00:12:06,459 --> 00:12:08,161
No, not you, her.

116
00:12:09,862 --> 00:12:12,031
The evil spirit hadn't
fully possessed her,

117
00:12:12,098 --> 00:12:12,965
she'll be okay.

118
00:12:13,032 --> 00:12:14,100
That's good.

119
00:12:15,168 --> 00:12:16,469
Um, boss...

120
00:12:17,070 --> 00:12:18,504
Things got pretty hairy earlier,

121
00:12:18,571 --> 00:12:19,939
I missed some shots in the end.

122
00:12:20,006 --> 00:12:21,374
What should I do?

123
00:12:21,441 --> 00:12:23,576
Have another take?
Should I wake them all up?

124
00:12:24,377 --> 00:12:26,445
No, we can't do that but
we need a proper ending.

125
00:12:26,512 --> 00:12:29,515
You should've shot properly!

126
00:12:30,416 --> 00:12:31,784
Yeah...

127
00:12:31,851 --> 00:12:33,419
Is Det. Choi on the way?

128
00:12:33,486 --> 00:12:35,021
Yes, he's heading over.

129
00:12:56,242 --> 00:12:59,345
I got a lot better thanks to you.

130
00:12:59,412 --> 00:13:03,015
I can breathe better,
thank you so much.

131
00:13:03,082 --> 00:13:04,483
I'm glad to hear it.

132
00:13:04,550 --> 00:13:06,752
You should still take your meds,

133
00:13:06,819 --> 00:13:09,889
and I'll drop the dosage
as I monitor the progress.

134
00:13:10,923 --> 00:13:12,325
Check up on her every 2 hours.

135
00:13:12,392 --> 00:13:13,393
Yes, doctor.

136
00:14:26,132 --> 00:14:27,066
(Exorcism)

137
00:14:27,133 --> 00:14:28,668
(Patient Clip)

138
00:14:30,403 --> 00:14:32,271
(Suspected of
Schizophrenia Day 142)

139
00:14:32,338 --> 00:14:34,207
(Exorcism Treatment Day 7)

140
00:14:45,184 --> 00:14:46,328
(The Man Who Punched
Out Four Gangs)

141
00:14:46,352 --> 00:14:47,420
(and Illegal Fight Clubs)

142
00:14:50,022 --> 00:14:52,625
(Are They Devils? Or Messiahs?)

143
00:14:53,393 --> 00:14:56,195
Catalina, it's fine.

144
00:14:56,763 --> 00:14:59,932
I'm making money to
build a Catholic orphanage.

145
00:15:01,267 --> 00:15:02,969
No need to thank me.

146
00:15:03,669 --> 00:15:06,739
Yeah, Catalina, okay.

147
00:15:08,040 --> 00:15:10,242
Boss, I found out
who those guys served.

148
00:15:10,309 --> 00:15:11,477
Who?

149
00:15:11,544 --> 00:15:12,845
Beelzebul.

150
00:15:12,912 --> 00:15:14,189
(Beelzebul: Chief
lieutenant of Lucifer)

151
00:15:14,213 --> 00:15:15,448
Who's their leader?

152
00:15:15,948 --> 00:15:17,783
I haven't found
their archbishop yet,

153
00:15:17,850 --> 00:15:20,619
but I got informants
all over the place.

154
00:15:20,686 --> 00:15:22,221
Ton of high-ranking demons

155
00:15:22,288 --> 00:15:24,357
like Beelzebul are popping up,

156
00:15:24,424 --> 00:15:27,126
a massive crisis may
be on the horizon.

157
00:15:27,627 --> 00:15:29,795
I've seen them countless times,

158
00:15:29,862 --> 00:15:30,996
but they still scare me.

159
00:15:31,063 --> 00:15:32,732
We're scared too.

160
00:15:32,799 --> 00:15:35,334
They're powered by demon's energy,

161
00:15:35,401 --> 00:15:37,837
so always keep your guard up.

162
00:15:38,671 --> 00:15:41,040
You still have a bright future.

163
00:15:43,543 --> 00:15:44,610
And me?

164
00:15:51,217 --> 00:15:52,285
Me?

165
00:15:55,154 --> 00:15:57,824
Is my future bleak?

166
00:16:00,626 --> 00:16:01,694
So hot today...

167
00:16:01,761 --> 00:16:02,294
Excuse me.

168
00:16:02,361 --> 00:16:03,696
Be gone!

169
00:16:04,363 --> 00:16:05,965
My apologies, who are you?

170
00:16:06,032 --> 00:16:07,433
May I help you?

171
00:16:08,100 --> 00:16:09,935
Could I meet the owner?

172
00:16:10,002 --> 00:16:12,572
Yes, I'm the owner,
what can I do for you?

173
00:16:13,339 --> 00:16:16,542
My sister is really sick.

174
00:16:17,043 --> 00:16:19,311
I came here because
I'm at wit's end.

175
00:16:19,378 --> 00:16:20,746
Did Det. Choi tell you about us?

176
00:16:20,813 --> 00:16:22,582
No, Father Mar...

177
00:16:24,417 --> 00:16:28,488
Father Marco recommended us?

178
00:16:31,190 --> 00:16:35,695
My apologies, we do
not work with them.

179
00:16:36,996 --> 00:16:38,064
I'm sorry.

180
00:16:40,032 --> 00:16:41,501
My sister is in danger!

181
00:16:42,034 --> 00:16:44,303
If you help us, I'll do anything.

182
00:16:45,071 --> 00:16:46,572
I brought money too.

183
00:16:47,206 --> 00:16:48,374
Here.

184
00:16:49,375 --> 00:16:50,376
If...

185
00:16:52,578 --> 00:16:56,482
If she's sick,
take her to the hospital.

186
00:16:56,549 --> 00:16:58,217
She should see
a neuropsychiatrist.

187
00:16:58,284 --> 00:17:00,286
I'm a neuropsychiatrist!

188
00:17:01,988 --> 00:17:03,322
Christ...

189
00:17:07,393 --> 00:17:08,528
Please...

190
00:17:13,699 --> 00:17:17,169
This contains her videos,

191
00:17:18,337 --> 00:17:20,072
please give it to him.

192
00:17:20,139 --> 00:17:21,574
I'm begging you.

193
00:17:22,575 --> 00:17:23,876
I understand.

194
00:17:49,936 --> 00:17:52,004
(Han Eun-seo)

195
00:17:54,006 --> 00:17:56,242
(Neuropsychiatry approach...)

196
00:18:03,916 --> 00:18:05,951
This is my sister and my home.

197
00:18:06,018 --> 00:18:08,754
Jung-won and Eun-seo's home.

198
00:18:08,821 --> 00:18:10,790
Let's live happily here.

199
00:18:11,591 --> 00:18:13,692
- Let's never fight.
- Yeah, let's not fight.

200
00:18:13,759 --> 00:18:15,461
Don't steal my clothes.

201
00:18:15,528 --> 00:18:17,129
Don't use my make-up.

202
00:18:20,666 --> 00:18:22,735
We moved today, so let's be happy.

203
00:18:22,802 --> 00:18:24,403
Let's be happy.

204
00:18:25,137 --> 00:18:27,673
- Thank you, sis.
- Not at all.

205
00:18:29,976 --> 00:18:30,843
You like it?

206
00:18:30,910 --> 00:18:33,279
Yeah, the air is so nice here.

207
00:19:16,155 --> 00:19:17,657
As a fellow doctor,

208
00:19:18,391 --> 00:19:21,394
I couldn't believe it
until I saw your sister.

209
00:19:22,395 --> 00:19:26,165
Since the Church
officially prohibits exorcism,

210
00:19:26,766 --> 00:19:28,668
I suggested you go to him.

211
00:19:29,702 --> 00:19:30,803
Of course, as a doctor,

212
00:19:30,870 --> 00:19:32,471
I know you must have had doubts...

213
00:19:33,773 --> 00:19:35,341
Devil, exorcism,

214
00:19:36,609 --> 00:19:38,210
I don't know about these things.

215
00:19:40,112 --> 00:19:44,350
I simply want to
save my sister, Father.

216
00:19:50,756 --> 00:19:52,091
- Hey.
- Yes?

217
00:19:53,592 --> 00:19:55,127
Where did Sharon go?

218
00:19:56,128 --> 00:19:57,630
She should be in her office.

219
00:19:59,198 --> 00:20:00,966
By the way, boss,

220
00:20:01,033 --> 00:20:02,401
do you want to see the footage

221
00:20:02,468 --> 00:20:03,869
that pretty doctor brought?

222
00:20:04,537 --> 00:20:06,271
Nah, forget it.

223
00:20:06,338 --> 00:20:08,507
But if Father Marco sent her,

224
00:20:08,574 --> 00:20:10,676
it could be something big.

225
00:20:10,743 --> 00:20:14,179
Don't ever mention
his name to me again.

226
00:20:14,246 --> 00:20:15,514
I'm sorry.

227
00:20:15,581 --> 00:20:17,516
Where's Sharon, I
need to give this to her.

228
00:20:17,583 --> 00:20:18,283
I'm right here.

229
00:20:18,350 --> 00:20:21,053
Holy Jesus! She's right here...

230
00:20:21,587 --> 00:20:24,290
Could you stop sneaking up on us?

231
00:20:25,124 --> 00:20:26,892
(Sharon Kim Goon)

232
00:20:26,959 --> 00:20:28,694
Here, here.

233
00:20:28,761 --> 00:20:30,562
Your salary, thank you as always.

234
00:20:30,629 --> 00:20:31,430
Good work.

235
00:20:31,497 --> 00:20:32,497
Here.

236
00:20:33,165 --> 00:20:34,233
Put it away.

237
00:20:34,300 --> 00:20:36,068
Why is mine so thin?

238
00:20:37,236 --> 00:20:39,405
Sharon's work is a lot tougher.

239
00:20:39,472 --> 00:20:41,674
She's got to perform
rites on blades and stuff.

240
00:20:41,741 --> 00:20:42,908
When do I ever do that?

241
00:20:42,975 --> 00:20:44,176
Anyway, she does a lot

242
00:20:44,243 --> 00:20:46,211
of really difficult tasks, thanks.

243
00:20:46,278 --> 00:20:47,413
Take it.

244
00:20:47,913 --> 00:20:50,049
Thank you, bud.

245
00:20:51,851 --> 00:20:54,019
Wait a minute.

246
00:20:54,086 --> 00:20:56,088
Demons and their worshippers

247
00:20:56,155 --> 00:20:59,091
are increasing and getting bolder.

248
00:20:59,158 --> 00:21:01,727
They flex in
the middle of the city.

249
00:21:01,794 --> 00:21:03,929
More and more people
are dying, am I right?

250
00:21:03,996 --> 00:21:07,867
And our workload
is growing too, right?

251
00:21:08,801 --> 00:21:12,838
So, how about a salary bump?

252
00:21:21,547 --> 00:21:25,117
It's been a while, hasn't it?
10 years already.

253
00:21:25,618 --> 00:21:27,319
You haven't changed at all.

254
00:21:29,155 --> 00:21:32,825
Of course, I've had
this face since I was 19.

255
00:21:35,528 --> 00:21:37,168
Your sense of humor
hasn't changed either.

256
00:21:40,633 --> 00:21:42,735
Dr. Han Jung-won
came by, didn't she?

257
00:21:43,769 --> 00:21:47,639
I know you refused because
of me, but her sister...

258
00:21:47,706 --> 00:21:51,610
I no longer want to
get involved with you.

259
00:21:52,711 --> 00:21:55,181
I know you still resent me.

260
00:21:56,215 --> 00:22:01,320
I struggled too, so many
lives were lost back then.

261
00:22:02,755 --> 00:22:04,824
But I didn't want to accept

262
00:22:05,724 --> 00:22:07,359
that Joseph was involved.

263
00:22:07,960 --> 00:22:10,029
The Joseph
we knew no longer exists.

264
00:22:10,696 --> 00:22:15,434
Only Lucifer, who killed
our angelic children

265
00:22:15,935 --> 00:22:17,636
and nuns, remains.

266
00:22:19,805 --> 00:22:21,207
The demon you raised.

267
00:22:22,875 --> 00:22:24,810
I prayed with regrets and tears.

268
00:22:26,111 --> 00:22:27,312
The will of God...

269
00:22:27,379 --> 00:22:28,848
Those children

270
00:22:31,016 --> 00:22:35,821
are all dead,
is that the will of God?

271
00:22:37,056 --> 00:22:42,127
Even if you can't forgive me,
can't you help her?

272
00:22:53,873 --> 00:22:54,873
Eun-seo!

273
00:23:02,581 --> 00:23:03,515
(Park, Kidnapped by
