I mean, I'm not a demon.

548
00:51:04,295 --> 00:51:05,596
Yes?

549
00:51:05,663 --> 00:51:07,030
Turn on the machine.

550
00:51:07,097 --> 00:51:08,499
Okay.

551
00:51:10,968 --> 00:51:12,570
Her vitals are
within normal range.

552
00:51:14,138 --> 00:51:15,539
Let's begin.

553
00:51:17,308 --> 00:51:19,410
You must answer all my questions.

554
00:51:20,244 --> 00:51:22,346
Or you will feel intense pain.

555
00:51:24,281 --> 00:51:25,215
(Jugwi: A bamboo
that wards off evil)

556
00:51:25,282 --> 00:51:27,518
Do not touch me, no!

557
00:51:27,585 --> 00:51:28,886
(and malevolent energies)

558
00:51:28,953 --> 00:51:30,220
Tell me your name!

559
00:51:30,287 --> 00:51:31,488
Tell me!

560
00:51:38,829 --> 00:51:39,763
What happened?

561
00:51:39,830 --> 00:51:41,465
We're entering 'Deception' stage.

562
00:51:41,532 --> 00:51:42,933
(Deception)

563
00:51:43,000 --> 00:51:44,735
The evil will try to deceive us.

564
00:52:08,592 --> 00:52:09,826
Jung-won...

565
00:52:09,893 --> 00:52:12,596
I'm so scared...

566
00:52:12,663 --> 00:52:15,199
Could you untie me?

567
00:52:28,312 --> 00:52:29,780
(Dongkyung: A small mirror imbued)

568
00:52:29,847 --> 00:52:31,248
(with the shaman's soul)

569
00:52:38,789 --> 00:52:42,526
(Taeju: An act to
convey the words)

570
00:52:42,593 --> 00:52:45,396
(of the guardian spirit)

571
00:52:56,640 --> 00:52:59,977
You want to know my name?
Should I tell you?

572
00:53:04,314 --> 00:53:06,083
The demon isn't pretending.

573
00:53:10,788 --> 00:53:13,557
Before existence,

574
00:53:14,258 --> 00:53:15,726
I was the first being.

575
00:53:20,164 --> 00:53:23,267
I am both one and infinite.

576
00:53:24,034 --> 00:53:26,170
I am eternity and finality.

577
00:53:27,371 --> 00:53:29,740
I am within you,

578
00:53:30,741 --> 00:53:35,212
I am not within you.

579
00:54:15,452 --> 00:54:17,488
The interior lights
are being shut off.

580
00:54:19,256 --> 00:54:20,624
Something's odd.

581
00:54:21,158 --> 00:54:23,060
I'll look into it,

582
00:54:24,328 --> 00:54:25,796
stay on guard.

583
00:54:27,030 --> 00:54:28,198
Okay.

584
00:54:58,328 --> 00:55:00,030
There you were.

585
00:55:04,134 --> 00:55:05,134
Dammit...

586
00:55:27,724 --> 00:55:32,496
I exist everywhere, and nowhere.

587
00:55:42,239 --> 00:55:43,841
You vile demon.

588
00:55:44,875 --> 00:55:47,611
Reveal your name at once,

589
00:55:48,412 --> 00:55:49,780
and expel from the girl.

590
00:56:23,046 --> 00:56:26,216
You're too chicken
to come in here.

591
00:56:26,283 --> 00:56:29,486
Come in, do it.

592
00:56:53,043 --> 00:56:57,247
Petty priests like you
can never defeat us.

593
00:57:33,283 --> 00:57:35,919
The demon within,

594
00:57:35,986 --> 00:57:37,955
release her at once!

595
00:57:38,588 --> 00:57:41,491
Expel yourself!

596
00:57:42,659 --> 00:57:44,795
The demon within,

597
00:57:45,963 --> 00:57:49,199
release her at once!

598
00:57:49,266 --> 00:57:51,368
Expel yourself!

599
00:58:20,497 --> 00:58:22,366
Hey, it's me.

600
00:58:23,033 --> 00:58:24,501
Boss, are you okay?

601
00:58:29,239 --> 00:58:30,407
Yeah, I'm fine now.

602
00:58:33,176 --> 00:58:35,312
Boss, I told you once before,

603
00:58:35,379 --> 00:58:38,281
always watch out for
the powder they throw at you.

604
00:58:38,348 --> 00:58:39,482
It could paralyze you,

605
00:58:39,549 --> 00:58:41,618
and you could even die from it.

606
00:58:41,685 --> 00:58:43,286
All right, get on with it.

607
00:58:43,987 --> 00:58:45,288
Okay.

608
00:58:50,694 --> 00:58:52,362
Now it's the third stage,
'Break Point'.

609
00:58:53,263 --> 00:58:56,099
You should use this moment
to get some rest.

610
00:58:57,768 --> 00:59:00,504
(Break Point)

611
00:59:03,040 --> 00:59:04,641
Jung-won?

612
00:59:08,812 --> 00:59:10,013
Are you okay?

613
00:59:20,624 --> 00:59:21,424
I command you

614
00:59:21,491 --> 00:59:23,226
in the name of our
almighty creators,

615
00:59:24,261 --> 00:59:26,329
return to the netherworld!

616
00:59:26,396 --> 00:59:27,531
Return at once!

617
00:59:33,336 --> 00:59:36,106
Jung-won, wake up!

618
00:59:37,641 --> 00:59:39,642
Doctor, it's okay,
everything's fine.

619
00:59:39,709 --> 00:59:42,646
The demon entered
your body momentarily.

620
00:59:43,847 --> 00:59:45,548
They sometimes
target a family member

621
00:59:45,615 --> 00:59:46,950
during the exorcism.

622
00:59:49,619 --> 00:59:51,421
There's something
else in the house.

623
01:00:40,203 --> 01:00:41,471
- Bud.
- Yes?

624
01:00:41,538 --> 01:00:42,839
Don't read that.

625
01:00:42,906 --> 01:00:44,007
Okay.

626
01:00:44,875 --> 01:00:46,643
What does it mean?

627
01:00:46,710 --> 01:00:47,944
I'm not sure.

628
01:00:48,879 --> 01:00:51,081
It's an ancient
language called 'Igbo'.

629
01:00:51,615 --> 01:00:54,217
This is why all these
unexpected events

630
01:00:54,284 --> 01:00:55,585
kept happening.

631
01:00:55,652 --> 01:00:57,721
There is a curse
on the entire house.

632
01:01:00,257 --> 01:01:02,225
What do we do then?

633
01:01:02,292 --> 01:01:04,461
We have to remove
all of these symbols.

634
01:01:41,765 --> 01:01:44,334
Did something happen to me?

635
01:01:46,469 --> 01:01:48,572
It felt like something
left my body.

636
01:01:49,639 --> 01:01:51,975
Eun-seo, are you okay?

637
01:01:52,042 --> 01:01:53,176
Feeling better?

638
01:01:53,243 --> 01:01:54,711
Wait.

639
01:01:56,947 --> 01:01:58,215
Jung-won...

640
01:02:02,919 --> 01:02:04,621
Could you untie me?

641
01:02:05,455 --> 01:02:08,591
Eun-seo, is that you?
Do you recognize me?

642
01:02:08,658 --> 01:02:09,826
Hold on.

643
01:02:29,946 --> 01:02:33,350
This idiot will die
one way or another.

644
01:02:36,219 --> 01:02:37,420
Remember?

645
01:02:38,822 --> 01:02:42,225
You let all those
poor children die.

646
01:02:44,427 --> 01:02:46,629
'Voice' stage has begun.

647
01:02:46,696 --> 01:02:49,366
(Voice)

648
01:02:51,801 --> 01:02:56,139
Mister, save me...

649
01:02:57,507 --> 01:02:59,709
Help me, Mr. Bow!

650
01:03:07,717 --> 01:03:12,522
Joseph killed them?
No, you killed them.

651
01:03:12,589 --> 01:03:16,059
They all died because
you couldn't stop him.

652
01:03:17,160 --> 01:03:20,430
Let's go visit him together.

653
01:03:20,497 --> 01:03:22,765
Then you can achieve eternal life.

654
01:03:22,832 --> 01:03:26,102
If not, you'll end up
killing this child too.

655
01:03:26,169 --> 01:03:27,804
Just like you
killed Sister Angela,

656
01:03:27,871 --> 01:03:28,871
your mother figure.

657
01:03:33,643 --> 01:03:39,849
Kill! Kill! Kill!

658
01:03:39,916 --> 01:03:41,918
- Kill!
- Boss!

659
01:03:42,452 --> 01:03:46,990
- Boss, boss, no!
- Kill!

660
01:03:50,393 --> 01:03:51,661
Sharon!

661
01:04:00,337 --> 01:04:03,740
Boss, I'm okay.

662
01:04:05,975 --> 01:04:07,544
Do not fall prey to its delusion.

663
01:04:17,987 --> 01:04:23,793
(Shindo: Daggers
imbued with a divine spirit)

664
01:04:47,117 --> 01:04:52,255
Why are you siding with humans?

665
01:04:52,322 --> 01:04:57,293
Your power did not come from him,

666
01:04:58,261 --> 01:05:01,364
but from my brother!

667
01:05:07,670 --> 01:05:10,840
If my power came
from your brother,

668
01:05:12,375 --> 01:05:17,981
it proves he couldn't defeat me.

669
01:05:19,082 --> 01:05:24,521
Do you think you can handle

670
01:05:25,422 --> 01:05:27,524
that much power?

671
01:05:54,918 --> 01:05:55,919
Here you go.

672
01:05:58,721 --> 01:06:00,089
What's this?

673
01:06:00,156 --> 01:06:01,257
A lid.

674
01:06:02,225 --> 01:06:03,426
Why did you bring a lid?

675
01:06:04,160 --> 01:06:05,762
You said to bring
something to cover.

676
01:06:07,030 --> 01:06:10,467
I meant a coat to cover
her body, you moron.

677
01:06:26,783 --> 01:06:28,451
Why do you waste your life

678
01:06:30,286 --> 01:06:33,556
on these pathetic beings?

679
01:06:34,591 --> 01:06:37,694
You know it eats away your body,

680
01:06:38,261 --> 01:06:40,897
as you use your power.

681
01:06:41,831 --> 01:06:43,633
You've felt it,

682
01:06:44,834 --> 01:06:47,570
is it worth saving these humans,

683
01:06:48,137 --> 01:06:49,839
who are wicked and greedy?

684
01:06:50,707 --> 01:06:53,009
Be with us, sister.

685
01:06:55,044 --> 01:06:56,713
Be with us.

686
01:06:57,514 --> 01:06:59,949
I am not your sister.

687
01:07:02,819 --> 01:07:04,521
Get out of my head!

688
01:07:20,904 --> 01:07:22,171
Reveal your name!

689
01:07:23,006 --> 01:07:24,741
I'll make this pain go away!

690
01:07:25,542 --> 01:07:28,144
Tell me your name, now!

691
01:07:30,780 --> 01:07:35,285
Tell me your name!

692
01:07:36,252 --> 01:07:37,921
Tell me!

693
01:07:39,055 --> 01:07:40,056
What's your name!

694
01:07:40,823 --> 01:07:42,525
Jung-won, please...

695
01:07:43,226 --> 01:07:44,160
Save me...

696
01:07:44,227 --> 01:07:45,227
Stop it! Please!

697
01:07:49,332 --> 01:07:50,266
- Jung-won!
- You can't!

698
01:07:50,333 --> 01:07:51,267
It's not over yet!

699
01:07:51,334 --> 01:07:52,569
The boundary...

700
01:08:19,262 --> 01:08:20,763
Wait.

701
01:08:24,267 --> 01:08:25,535
Step back.

702
01:08:48,725 --> 01:08:51,694
She is mine now.

703
01:09:15,918 --> 01:09:17,520
We're now in 'Clash' stage.

704
01:09:17,587 --> 01:09:18,888
We need to find her quickly.

705
01:09:18,955 --> 01:09:22,091
(Clash)

706
01:09:26,496 --> 01:09:27,864
Sharon...

707
01:09:41,944 --> 01:09:43,446
With your power,

708
01:09:44,247 --> 01:09:46,449
we can rule the world.

709
01:09:47,417 --> 01:09:49,352
Be with us, sister.

710
01:09:51,154 --> 01:09:53,556
Be with us.

711
01:10:27,990 --> 01:10:29,425
Boss, we're locked in!

712
01:10:29,492 --> 01:10:31,027
Move out of the way.

713
01:10:31,794 --> 01:10:34,797
I'm doing a lot of
home degrading today.

714
01:10:42,238 --> 01:10:43,673
Wait, boss!

715
01:10:43,740 --> 01:10:44,740
What is it?

716
01:10:49,746 --> 01:10:51,047
It's an automatic door.

717
01:10:52,248 --> 01:10:53,683
Dammit...

718
01:10:57,420 --> 01:10:58,621
Jung-won...

719
01:11:10,933 --> 01:11:13,669
Eun-seo, are you in there?

720
01:11:34,891 --> 01:11:36,159
- Jung-won!
- Eun-seo!

721
01:11:51,874 --> 01:11:53,042
Hey, hey!

722
01:12:04,287 --> 01:12:05,755
- Are you okay?
- You good?

723
01:12:07,290 --> 01:12:08,824
I'm fine, doctor...

724
01:12:08,891 --> 01:12:11,227
Is there a room
we don't know about?

725
01:12:14,096 --> 01:12:18,234
We moved all our big furniture

726
01:12:18,301 --> 01:12:21,838
into the shed out back.

727
01:12:24,173 --> 01:12:25,173
Shed...

728
01:12:44,293 --> 01:12:45,628
Over there!

729
01:12:53,903 --> 01:12:55,338
What's that?

730
01:12:56,505 --> 01:12:58,574
The demon is taking
more control over her.

731
01:13:20,696 --> 01:13:21,564
Eun-seo...

732
01:13:21,631 --> 01:13:23,132
Doctor, no! No!

733
01:13:55,164 --> 01:13:56,732
So, this is where you hang out.

734
01:14:09,445 --> 01:14:11,380
Wounded soul,

735
01:14:11,447 --> 01:14:14,016
why do you use the power

736
01:14:14,083 --> 01:14:16,319
devil has given you on humans?

737
01:14:19,155 --> 01:14:20,556
Are you Korean?

738
01:14:21,624 --> 01:14:26,963
If you interfere with us,
only death awaits you.

739
01:15:39,602 --> 01:15:42,138
Go, kill Sharon.

740
01:15:50,813 --> 01:15:53,416
Die, die, feel the terror.

741
01:15:57,086 --> 01:15:59,688
Die, die, feel the terror.

742
01:16:14,837 --> 01:16:19,575
Bow! Die!

743
01:17:11,127 --> 01:17:12,962
Die!

744
01:17:23,572 --> 01:17:24,807
Sharon!

745
01:17:42,291 --> 01:17:43,325
Boss...

746
01:17:45,594 --> 01:17:47,262
Blood, you're bleeding!

747
01:17:47,329 --> 01:17:48,697
What do we do, boss?

748
01:18:02,878 --> 01:18:05,748
I am your Omega.

749
01:18:09,285 --> 01:18:11,420
You are my Alpha.

750
01:18:16,792 --> 01:18:20,196
I am the new path.

751
01:18:22,932 --> 01:18:24,500
With my kingdom

752
01:18:24,567 --> 01:18:26,001
created with blood of children,

753
01:18:28,404 --> 01:18:30,539
I will rule you all.

754
01:18:42,151 --> 01:18:43,719
Now I get it.

755
01:18:45,387 --> 01:18:47,156
I know who you are.

756
01:18:48,624 --> 01:18:50,459
We're in the final stage,
'Expulsion'.

757
01:18:51,493 --> 01:18:54,129
After this stage,
we can save Eun-seo.

758
01:18:55,798 --> 01:19:01,804
A foul deity of death
that takes child sacrifices.

759
01:19:04,640 --> 01:19:05,640
Moloch!

760
01:19:12,581 --> 01:19:14,750
Your time is up.

761
01:19:45,347 --> 01:19:47,716
Return to where you came from!

762
01:19:47,783 --> 01:19:50,252
I expel you, Moloch!

763
01:19:50,819 --> 01:19:52,854
Return to hell at once!

764
01:19:52,921 --> 01:19:54,857
Return to hell, Moloch!

765
01:19:58,527 --> 01:20:00,529
Return to where you came from!

766
01:20:01,030 --> 01:20:02,865
I expel you, Moloch!

767
01:20:03,699 --> 01:20:05,501
Return to hell at once!

768
01:20:06,335 --> 01:20:08,304
Return to hell, Moloch!

769
01:20:10,005 --> 01:20:11,440
I expel you, Moloch!

770
01:20:15,544 --> 01:20:17,446
Return to where you came from!

771
01:20:18,414 --> 01:20:20,115
I expel you, Moloch!

772
01:20:30,993 --> 01:20:33,028
Return to hell!

773
01:20:34,129 --> 01:20:36,298
At once, Moloch!

774
01:20:37,966 --> 01:20:39,435
I expel you!

775
01:20:48,243 --> 01:20:50,412
- Eun-seo!
- Not yet!

776
01:20:51,280 --> 01:20:52,848
The demon is being expelled.

777
01:21:25,047 --> 01:21:29,851
Defeated by petty exorcists!

778
01:21:29,918 --> 01:21:35,624
I will one day shred you all!

779
01:21:39,128 --> 01:21:44,867
And I am taking
this idiot to hell.

780
01:21:45,934 --> 01:21:48,203
She's mine.

781
01:21:56,779 --> 01:21:57,913
Eun-seo!

782
01:21:58,414 --> 01:21:59,548
Sharon!

783
01:22:17,800 --> 01:22:19,735
Eun-seo! No! No!

784
01:22:32,514 --> 01:22:33,514
No!

785
01:22:48,130 --> 01:22:49,130
No!

786
01:22:54,970 --> 01:22:56,004
Sharon!

787
01:23:01,210 --> 01:23:04,513
I am the Grim Reaper!

788
01:23:04,580 --> 01:23:07,883
Leave the child alone,

789
01:23:09,451 --> 01:23:13,255
Valac's incarnation
is ordering you!

790
01:23:13,322 --> 01:23:15,657
Return to hell!

791
01:23:18,327 --> 01:23:20,595
Your time is almost up!

792
01:23:20,662 --> 01:23:23,598
If you want to live,

793
01:23:23,665 --> 01:23:26,435
accept the power of hell!

794
01:23:45,654 --> 01:23:49,491
Return to hell, Moloch!

795
01:24:54,289 --> 01:24:56,224
Eun-seo...

796
01:24:56,925 --> 01:24:57,925
Eun-seo?

797
01:25:07,703 --> 01:25:09,171
Can you hear me?

798
01:25:11,974 --> 01:25:13,241
Jung-won...

799
01:25:22,017 --> 01:25:23,552
I'm so sorry...

800
01:25:50,379 --> 01:25:53,481
(Don Lee)

801
01:25:53,548 --> 01:25:56,651
(Seohyun David Lee)

802
01:25:56,718 --> 01:25:59,488
(Gyeong Su Jin Jung Zi So)

803
01:26:01,289 --> 01:26:04,159
(Grand Opening of
Angela Orphanage)

804
01:26:04,226 --> 01:26:06,061
I'm taking the photo, look here!

805
01:26:06,128 --> 01:26:07,262
Everyone, smile!

806
01:26:07,329 --> 01:26:09,865
One, two, three!

807
01:26:13,201 --> 01:26:15,270
That's enough, kids.

808
01:26:15,337 --> 01:26:18,874
Bow, please come by
when you get a chance.

809
01:26:21,076 --> 01:26:22,711
- Let's move.
- Okay.

810
01:26:22,778 --> 01:26:23,879
Yes, sir.

